<p>Additional programs include the Residential Energy Efficiency Loan Program offering low-interest financing for energy improvements, and PACE financing options that allow property owners to finance solar and HVAC upgrades through property tax assessments. These combined incentives can reduce total project costs by 40-50%, making comprehensive energy upgrades highly attractive for Sacramento homeowners.</p>

